T02TD3528E:170b-1: aom di y'a na m'a r'i tsyee s'a dha nam /
T02TD3528E:170b-3: aom di y'a na'i 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3528E:170b-4: 'phags ma 'od zer can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3528E:170b-5: ao di y'a na'i 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs su gyur pa ni /
T02TD3528E:170b-6: dang por re zhig rang gi snying gar aom yig yongs su gyur pa las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
T02TD3528E:170b-7: de'i steng du dang po'i bcu gsum pa'i sa bon las zla phyed dang thig les brgyan pa'o //
T02TD3528E:170b-8: de bzhin du yang sdig pa thams cad so sor bshags pa la sogs pa byas nas /
T02TD3528E:170b-9: des de bzhin du bskyed pa'i mam yig / de yongs su gyur pa las 'od zer can sku mdog dmar mo zhal drug pa phyag bcu gnyis pa ste /
T02TD3528E:170b-10: zhal dang po ni dmar po /
T02TD3528E:170b-15: dbu'i steng du gnas pa ni phyag zhal nag po ste /
T02TD3528E:170b-19: rnam par snang mdzad ser pos mgon du byas pa /
T02TD3528E:170b-20: lto ba 'phyang zhing thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan pa /
T02TD3528E:170b-21: skra kham pa gyen du brdzes pa /
T02TD3528E:170b-22: sprul gyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3528E:170b-23: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
T02TD3528E:170b-24: g-yon brkyang gis phag dang bgegs mnan pa /
T02TD3528E:170b-25: phyag g-yas pa rnams kyis ral gri dang /
T02TD3528E:170b-29: rdo rje rtse gcig pa dang sta gri bsnams pa'o ;
T02TD3528E:170b-30: / g-yon rnams kyis sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhags pa dang /
T02TD3528E:170b-32: mya ngan med pa'i yal ga dang /
T02TD3528E:170b-36: spyan gsum pa dmar la zlum pa /
T02TD3528E:170b-37: zhal mche ba gtsigs pa shing rta'i dbus su bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD3528E:171a-2: sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhags pa dang /
T02TD3528E:171a-3: mya ngan med pa'i yal ga bsnams pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3528E:171a-4: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das ma'i phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3528E:171a-5: rdo rje'i thal mo sbyar nas ting nge 'dzin gyis gung me dag bkug nas mthe bong gnyis skyil krung rtse mo bkug nas bzung ba'o //
T02TD3528E:171a-6: sngags ni aom m'a r'i tsyee m'am h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3528E:171a-7: sku mdog dmar mo phyag bcu gnyis pa ao di y'a na'i 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
